# Sushi Rice

Based on [https://instantpot.com/blogs/...](https://instantpot.com/blogs/recipes/perfect-sushi-rice) and [Best Way To Make Sushi At Home - Epicurious](https://youtu.be/nIoOv6lWYnk)

